One of best beers in Korea. The aroma is awesome, it reminds me the summer night in Hawaii (since Ive never been there) Appearance is also wonderful, which looks like rainbow-unicorns golden glattering urine. Easy to drink, tastes like heaven. Also dont forget even children can drink this- Its like nektar! Elixir!!- 
Overall-This is freaking total legend.
